description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Garden at Sainte-Adresse / Claude Monet
-Tulpenfelder in Sassenheim / Claude Monet
-The Poppies / Claude Monet
-Irises / Vincent van Gogh
-Almond Blossoms / / Vincent van Gogh
-The Enchanted Garden / John William Waterhouse
-Dutch Flower Girl / George Hitchcock
-Flowers in Three Vases / Albert Dubois-Pillet
-The Roses of Heliogabalus / Lawrence Alma-Tadema
-A Lady in a Lilac Dress with Flowers / Władysław Czachórski
name: Masterpieces of World  - Brimming with Flowers -
